---------trust score :
Completeness (25pts) — how many key fields (description, equipment, etc.) are filled
Consistency (30pts) — starts full, deducted if contradictions found (e.g. clinic claiming 50+ beds, surgery without anaesthesiologist)
Verifiability (25pts) — how many specific equipment/procedures are mentioned
Recency (10pts) — whether page update date exists
Digital presence (10pts) — social media count
--------------



